    <h1>The Legacy of Tetris: Our Inspiration</h1>
    <br><br><br>

    <img src="images/screenshot.png" alt="Our project" class="float-left">
    <p class="justify"><a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=what+is+tetris&sca_esv=3f34b2bd337bbe02&sca_upv=1&biw=1536&bih=738&ei=y2ZwZquNM6uB9u8P-eOqsAs&ved=0ahUKEwjrnq_kieOGAxWrgP0HHfmxCrYQ4dUDCBA&uact=5&oq=what+is+tet&gs_&sclient=gws-wiz-serp" class="styled-link" target="_blank">Tetris</a>, one of the most iconic video games of all time, was created by Alexey Pajitnov, a Russian software engineer, in 1984. The game was born out of Pajitnov's love for puzzles and his desire to create an engaging yet simple game. Working at the Dorodnitsyn Computing Centre of the Soviet Academy of Sciences in Moscow, he developed Tetris on an Electronika 60 computer. The game's name is a combination of "tetromino" (the geometric shapes composed of four squares) and "tennis," Pajitnov's favorite sport. Tetris quickly gained popularity within the Soviet Union and soon captured the attention of the world. By the late 1980s, it had become a global phenomenon, especially after its release on the Nintendo Game Boy in 1989, which cemented its place in gaming history.</p>
    <p class="justify">The legacy of Tetris extends beyond its addictive gameplay, serving as a profound source of inspiration for our web application, TetraDashðŸ’¨. Tetris is celebrated not only for its simple yet challenging mechanics but also for its significant impact on the gaming industry and popular culture. The game's enduring appeal across multiple generations and platforms highlights its timeless nature. Tetris has influenced countless other games and has even been used in psychological studies to understand cognitive processes and assist in treating conditions like PTSD and addiction. Holding several Guinness World Records, including "Most Ported Video Game" and "Best-Selling Game on Early Generation Mobile Phones," Tetris's influence is undeniable. Inspired by this classic, we aim to capture the same spirit of innovation and enjoyment in TetraDashðŸ’¨, bringing a fresh yet familiar experience to modern audiences.</p>

